OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,FA woodland in the New Forest which is
OL,7,Frenowned for its bluebells has been
OL,8,Fwiped out by tree felling with
OL,9,Fcampaigners fearing for the wildlife
OL,10,Fthat live there.
OL,12,FMuch of the logging at the woods at
OL,13,FBroomy Inclosure took place during
OL,14,Frecent wet weather and campaigners say
OL,15,Fthe work has affected rare birds and
OL,16,Fis likely to have decimated the
OL,17,Fbluebells - which attract thousand of
OL,18,Fvisitors every year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
