PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,FForestry England authorised the work,
OL,7,Fwhich has been underway over the past
OL,8,Fcouple of months.
OL,10,FCommoner Ailsa Farrand fears what was
OL,11,Fspecial here has now been lost for
OL,12,Fever.
OL,14,F"The logging has gone through the
OL,15,Fbluebell woods, left all the brush
OL,16,Flying on top," she said.
OL,18,F"When it rained, I noticed all the
OL,19,Fbluebell bulbs were actually running
OL,20,Fthrough the water and down into the
OL,21,Fstream below.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,F"So they're actually lost to the site.
OL,8,F"I'm seeing it time and time again
OL,9,Fwhere not enough care is taken to
OL,10,Fpreserve this beautiful, protected
OL,11,Fsupposedly area."
OL,13,FSue Boyd is a keen bird watcher and is
OL,14,Fespecially concerned about the very
OL,15,Frare Eurasian Goshawk - which builds
OL,16,Fits nest in high and hidden locations
OL,17,F- now exposed by the work of the
OL,18,Floggers.
OL,20,F"They know they're there, and they
OL,21,Fhave actually marked the trees.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,F"But the contractors have driven
OL,7,Fdirectly beneath the trees, over the
OL,8,Froots of the trees, damaged the roots
OL,9,Fof the trees.
OL,11,F"Those trees will probably die until
OL,12,Fnow, along with the nest."
OL,14,FThe location, in the north of the New
OL,15,FForest, is popular with bike riders
OL,16,Fand walkers and many are shocked by
OL,17,Fwhat they've seen - including Phil
OL,18,FWade from the First Wessex Charity
OL,19,FWalking Group.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,F"It's completely changed the
OL,7,Fcomplexion of the forest here," he
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"It was very, very wooded before, and
OL,11,Fnow it's pretty desolate, as you can
OL,12,Fsee from the logs behind me."
OL,14,FPeople who work in the forest
OL,15,Funderstand that it does need to be
OL,16,Fmanaged, but senior Verderer Anthony
OL,17,FPasmore says this destruction and
OL,18,Fpollution amounts to negligence by
OL,19,FForestry England.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,F"It's land which is protected by all
OL,7,Fsorts of conservation designations.
OL,9,F"They can do this and they grumble
OL,10,Fabout a family car parked on the verge
OL,11,Fbecause it's destroying a few blades
OL,12,Fof grass.
OL,14,F"These are enormous ruts over huge
OL,15,Farea. They know perfectly well that
OL,16,Fthey are not obtaining proper reports
OL,17,Fin advance. If they were and if they
OL,18,Fwere observing them, then the damage
OL,19,Fsimply wouldn't happen."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,FForestry England has confirmed that
OL,7,Fwork has stopped because of the damage
OL,8,Fbeing caused to the environment.
OL,10,FA spokesperson said: "We can confirm
OL,11,Fthat timber harvesting in Broomy
OL,12,FInclosure have been stopped due to
OL,13,Fenvironmental damage caused by the
OL,14,Fcontractor.
OL,16,F"We are carrying out a full
OL,17,Finvestigation into the incident, its
OL,18,Fimpact and actions that need to be
OL,19,Ftaken.
OL,26,@rD@VOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773087073
OL,3,CFears for wildlife after New Forest
OL,4,Cbluebell wood wiped out by tree felling
OL,6,F"We will take any necessary actions we
OL,7,Fcan in the short term and a full
OL,8,Freinstatement of the site will take
OL,9,Fplace when weather conditions allow
OL,10,Flater in the year.
OL,12,FWe understand this incident may raise
OL,13,Fserious concerns and are taking this
OL,14,Fmatter extremely seriously."
